{"lemma":"نَهْباً","slug":"نَهْباً","root":"ن.ه.ب","root_slug":"ن-ه-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ن-ه-ب","pos":"ADV","pos_camel":"adv","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n40598"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%86%D9%8E%D9%87%D9%92%D8%A8%D8%A7%D9%8B"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to rob"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/na.ha.ba/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n40598","headword_ar":"نَهْبٌ","root":"nhb","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Spoil; plunder; booty;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuhobapN","text_ar":"نُهْبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA, art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xls","text_ar":"خلس"},{"kind":"text","text":":) ex."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ataY lahu binahobK","text_ar":"اَتَى لَهُ بِنَهْبٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he came to him with,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"brought to him, spoil:"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2856},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nihaAbN","text_ar":"نِهَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuhuwb","text_ar":"نُهُوب"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Nh, &c:) ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuhobaY","text_ar":"نُهْبَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the same;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and thus is similar to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuHolaY","text_ar":"نُحْلَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaTiy~apN","text_ar":"عَطِيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is allowed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"given, to be taken as spoil, plunder,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"booty;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and thus is similar to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EumoraY","text_ar":"عُمْرَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruqobaY","text_ar":"رُقْبَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (IAth;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuhobapN","text_ar":"نُهْبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb) [and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuhayobaY","text_ar":"نُهَيْبَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuh~ayobaY","text_ar":"نُهَّيْبَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":":] a man, named Fizr, said of some goats which he drove forth,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hiYa Aln~uh~ayobaY","text_ar":"هِىَ النُّهَّيْبَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~uhayobaY","text_ar":"النُّهَيْبَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", accord. to different readings; meaning that it was not allowable to any one person to take of them more than one (TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nahobN","text_ar":"نَهْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is taken as spoil, plunder,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"booty;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so taken by whomsoever will, of what is allowed to be so taken:"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA A@notuhiba","text_ar":"مَا ا@نْتُهِبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Lh, K:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuhobaY","text_ar":"نُهْبَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is allowed to be so taken;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_isomu maA A^unohiba","text_ar":"اـِسْمُ مَا اُنْهِبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is taken as spoil, plunder,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"booty;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_isomu maA nuhiba","text_ar":"اـِسْمُ مَا نُهِبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (So in one copy of the S.) ―         -b2-  [Hence]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nahobN","text_ar":"نَهْبٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An incursion made into an enemy's territory for the sake of acquiring spoil, plunder,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"booty; and a spoiling,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plundering."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHorazotu nahobiY waA^abotagiY Aln~awaAfila","text_ar":"اَحْرَزْتُ نَهْبِى وَاَبْتَغِى النَّوَافِلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in a trad. of Aboo-Beker, means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I have accomplished what I had to perform of the prayers termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alwitoru","text_ar":"الوِتْرُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"before my sleeping, lest the occasion for my doing so should slip from me; and when I awake, I perform the prayers termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlnwAfl","text_ar":"النوافل"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) [He termed the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wtr","text_ar":"وتر"},{"kind":"text","text":"prayers"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nahobN","text_ar":"نَهْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"because he performed them before the right time.]       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nahobN","text_ar":"نَهْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A kind of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rakoD","text_ar":"رَكْض"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e., app., of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"running,"},{"kind":"text","text":"with reference to a horse]. (Lh, K.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","S","K","Msb","Lh"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}